---
title: The templates to build microservices
---

<div class="pure-g">

  <div class="pure-u-1">
    <p>The following is a list of templates that can be used to build your own
    microservices that follow the MSA standard. Each one links to a github repo,
    that you can clone and modify to suit your needs.</p>
  </div>

  <% data.templates.templates.each do |f| %>
      <div class="pure-u-1 pure-u-md-1-2 pure-u-lg-1-3">
          <h1><a href="/microservices/<%= f.name %>"><%= f.name %></a></h1>
            <p class="ms-description"><%= f.description %></p>
      </div>
  <% end %>

</div>
